Package dsiter.iterator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDatasetIterator  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayIterator
    An iterator over an array.
    FilterIterator
    An iterator which uses a TypedRowAccessor.BOOLEAN to filter values from a source iterator.
    FirstIterator
    An iterator that returns only the first element of another source iterator.
    IteratorCounter  
    LastIterator
    An iterator that only returns the last element of another source iterator
    RangeIterator
    An iterator over a range of integers.
    RenameIterator
    An iterator that renames one of the columns of its source iterator.
    SkipIterator
    An iterator that skips the first howMany elements of its source iterator, and then returns the rest.
    StrideIterator
    Construct an iterator that only returns 1 in every stride rows from its source iterator.
    TakeIterator  
    ZipIterator
